Package: baseRpipe
Title: Use Base R Pipe Operator
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Chuanping", "Zhao", email = "zcphbumaster@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package enhances the usability of the base R pipe operator ('|>') by providing an RStudio add-in that allows users to insert the pipe operator into their scripts via a keyboard shortcut. The package aims to streamline coding workflows in RStudio by simplifying the insertion of the pipe, thereby improving coding efficiency and readability.
